{"type": "article", "id": 25307, "title": "Stellar Works 新系列", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-12T06:35:01Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 23, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702134953IaVDw7kz3YmAMUst.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是美国设计师 David Rockwell 为家具品牌 Stellar Works 设计的家具组，主要使用金属结构、深色的木材和皮革这三种材料制作了 14 件家具，多用在客厅等需要招待客人的环境，能体现出昂贵的价格、精致的做工和实用性。比如斜靠在墙上的金属架子，依次连接了六边形的镜子、一块置物的木板和皮革做的口袋，简洁有序而又有装饰性。旁边的皮凳有一个用皮革做的灵活的口袋，可以用来放杂志或包。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134949SLYJdlCRxyOUWb7g.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"1.39957265\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134950tMlko2ZUKyXV6WOS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134951JMWv1C9HKSIPR5Ld.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021349516D0l1jOKVbJa53z2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.40064103\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134952uN0qeRfbLadQcsiS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.40064103\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134953RONcXYeQGUwod381.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.40064103\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}